subsection.content:
For the purposes of subsection (3), the tribunal shall have powers similar to
                those vested in the Court of First Instance for hearing evidence, determining claims
                for damages and awarding costs. (Amended 92 of 1975 s. 59; 25 of 1998 s. 2)

